{"tid":1055960,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺個「狗」字好容易令人誤會","createTime":"2019-03-11T00:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T03:37:20.000Z","uid":79435,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9896597947ff1402353f96d3530770ca67d032","tid":1055960,"uid":79435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:46:59.000Z","msg":"狗明明咁可愛 咁多人鍾意<br />\n做有錢佬嘅狗 好過做窮人<br />\n但啲人都係會用個狗字去鬧人<br />\n咁可能會有令人誤會嘅時候 <br />\n例如你想鬧人做傳銷好仆街 嗌佢做傳銷狗<br />\n但佢可能會以為你話佢好忠心 真係為你著想<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議 應該要搵一種無人鍾意嘅動物去取代<br />\n例如係蚊<br />\n例句：你隻打靶傳銷蚊！ 咁就可以減少造成誤會嘅機會啦"},{"pid":"c2ea2bb0099b4c8326785d91f5971f2a9a2475c9","tid":1055960,"uid":179979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"其實我都應該要改下把口<br />\n唔好成日大陸狗前大陸狗後<br />\n狗咁忠心唔可以用落大陸狗到<br />\n咁有咩意見可以代替<br />\n大陸西？<br />\n大陸哩（唔夠強）"},{"pid":"da4046938ff15bfa7d62d7f5fa96df87d05aa804","tid":1055960,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c2ea2bb0099b4c8326785d91f5971f2a9a2475c9","tid":1055960,"uid":179979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"其實我都應該要改下把口<br />\n唔好成日大陸狗前大陸狗後<br />\n狗咁忠心唔可以用落大陸狗到<br />\n咁有咩意見可以代替<br />\n大陸西？<br />\n大陸哩（唔夠強）"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:51:58.000Z","msg":"不嬲叫開蝗蟲架喎...<br />\n你新香港人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933df6233529c9392a9242e510468021ad071c89","tid":1055960,"uid":15758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"立即駁嘴"},{"pid":"027ead28ee1652b7bb1d4b77c4f8f8b8734d5fab","tid":1055960,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:01:00.000Z","msg":"叫內地人ok?"},{"pid":"bdfd6a226e682378e86a6211464ced5a2ac1c9ca","tid":1055960,"uid":179979,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da4046938ff15bfa7d62d7f5fa96df87d05aa804","tid":1055960,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c2ea2bb0099b4c8326785d91f5971